message.body: Hey if i move to minnesota, do i need 4wheel drive on a vehicle? P.S. Glad you're liking school so much! =)
Chloe! I haven't ever had a vehicle with 4 wheel drive, so def not necessary. Are you moving here?!?!
=) Possibly UM =) coming for an interview in a few weeks =)
Oh man, I wish I was there to see you! Gack. What are you studying? And do you have a place to stay etc?
School psych and no place yet. I'm also interviewing at wisconsin-madison so it's not 100% yet =) but i'm excited! I wish you'd be there so i could see you too!
I'll check with my free-ends about a place to stay or at least a few friendly faces to get coffee with! And such good luck to you. :)
Thanks! I had to say free-ends out loud cause it was so fun =) and good luck to you in school!! I'm glad you like it and the people so much!
